<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Mike_Oldfield&action=edit&section=13.php.html" title="Edit section: Quotation">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Quotation">Quotation</span></h2>
<blockquote class="templatequote">
<div class="Bug6200">People are very complicated machines – to get them to do what you want, you have to be very careful. You have to behave towards them in a very definite sequence.</div>
<div class="templatequotecite">—<i><a href="NME" title="NME">NME</a></i> – April 1979<sup id="cite_ref-NME_Rock_.27N.27_Roll_Years_53-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-NME_Rock_.27N.27_Roll_Years-53"><span>[</span>53<span>]</span></a></sup></div>
</blockquote>
