<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Mike_Oldfield&action=edit&section=15.php.html" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Bibliography">Bibliography</span></h2>
<ul>
